Now we can eliminate <code>@empty</code> (which means we can eliminate <code>initialize</code> as well).

<ruby>
class Stack
  def empty?
    @item.nil?
  end
  def push item
    @item = item
  end
  def top
     @item
  end
end
</ruby>

